node.text:
Woooo!!! 2x @illustratedworldseries champion!!! What an amazing event!!! Thank you Marc for letting me be apart of it even under some unfortunate circumstances! And all the competitors for bringing some tough competition and pushing me even more! Thank you everyone that also helped by voting for the social vote!  @curtiscreationz @boyishmind @keomatch @kingtrou 

Scroll to see the 1hr drawing from the competition 

Can’t wait for the future competitions! 

And thank you to the sponsors for making this event even better! @samsunguk @buzzfeeduk @twitch @scrawlrbox @thetoychronicle @brutmagazine @artgeckosketch 

#iwslive #illustrator #art #competition #drawing #sketch #doodle #alexsolis
